      "date": "2013-05-21 12:59:54.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/504f9fb8-c216-11e2-a892-52540035b04c).  Ran 1 tests.  1 tests failed: node-provisioning-1.",
